I '''Brillante Mendoza''' (mibait Julio 30, 1960) metung yang Filipinong [[direktor pelikula]].<ref name="CNN">{{cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Movies/08/13/brilliante.mendoza/index.html |title=Brilliante Mendoza: Philippines' celebrated and divisive director |accessdate=2009-05-09 |work=CNN}}</ref> Mibait ya ampong meragul king San Fernando, Pampanga. Kinangwa yang Advertising Arts king kanita College of Architecture and Fine Arts ning [[University of Santo Tomas]].<ref name="varsitarian">{{cite web |url=http://varsitarian.net/circle/20120819/pagdukot_sa_mga_burnham_isinapelikula |title=Pagdukot sa mga Burnham, isinapelikula |accessdate=2012-10-20 |work=varsitarian}}</ref>
[[File:BrillanteMendozaCannesMay09.jpg|thumb|right|200px|Mendoza won Best Director at the [[2009 Cannes Film Festival|62nd Cannes Film Festival]] for his film ''[[Kinatay]]''.]]

Mig-direktor ne kareng labing-anam a pelikula manibat anyang 2005. Simbut ne ing galal a [[Best Director Award (Cannes Film Festival)|Best Director]] para king pelikulang ''[[Kinatay]]'' king [[2009 Cannes Film Festival|62nd Cannes Film Festival]].<ref name="festival-cannes.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.com/en/archives/ficheFilm/id/10901054/year/2009.html |title=Festival de Cannes: Kinatay |accessdate=2009-05-09|work=festival-cannes.com}}</ref> Ing pelikula na kanitang 2009, ing ''Lola'' sinambut yang galal a Best Film king  6th [[Dubai International Film Festival]].<ref name="dubaifilmfest">{{cite web |url=http://www.dubaifilmfest.com/index.php/en/past-edition/year-2009/winners/ |title= Dubai International Film Festival – 2009 Winners |accessdate=2011-07-24|work=dubaifilmfest.com}}</ref> Ing pelikula na anyang 2012, ing ''[[Captive (2012 film)|Captive]]'', pepalage de king kumpetisyun king [[62nd Berlin International Film Festival]] anyang Febrero 2012.<ref name="Berlin">{{cite web|url=http://www.berlinale.de/en/presse/pressemitteilungen/alle/Alle-Detail_11860.html |title=First Films for the Competition and Berlinale Special |accessdate=2011-12-20 |work=Berlin Film Festival}}</ref>

